data.description: Welcome to your next home in Brookhaven!  The spacious living area provides the perfect space for entertaining guests or enjoying cozy evenings with your loved ones. Retreat to the luxurious master suite boasting a generous layout, Three additional well-appointed bedrooms offer plenty of space for family members or can be transformed into a home office, gym, or hobby room to suit your needs. The outdoor space could become your oasis beckoning you to unwind and enjoy the beautiful Alabama weather. The backyard is perfect for hosting barbecues and outdoor gatherings, while the covered patio provides a peaceful retreat for morning coffee or evening relaxation with a glass of wine.  Tucked away at the end of the cul-de-sac this home allows you the convenience and fun of a neighborhood and the privacy you seek after a long day.  The neighborhood has a pool and a clubhouse, a basketball court, and a stocked lake all ready for you to enjoy this summer and all year!  It's time to make a move!
